Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:25.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}割り切れない想いを力に変えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:29.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無謀だと笑われた　何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:33.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}毎日が冒険で　青春で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:38.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい音と出会っては磨いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:42.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}本気でやったからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こわい瞬間もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:47.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:48.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:49.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:50.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:55.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一度息を吹き込む　明日へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:59.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}タクトに導かれてここまで来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:03.50,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:05.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でているのは人生だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:07.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響くのは感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:12.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと忘れないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:16.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}光る音が涙を照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:21.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛いことばかりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:26.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だっていつも　いつも楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そうでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:32.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！歌え　五線の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:39.37,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！響け　遠くの春に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:25.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春的苦涩变为了前进的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:29.84,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}年少冲动让我无数次被嘲笑声掩埋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:33.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天都在冒险　挥洒青春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:38.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断磨练期待与新的乐声邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:42.48,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为全身心的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自然会有害怕的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:47.96,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要传递
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:48.86,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:49.66,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:50.44,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:55.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次向着奏响的明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:59.45,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遵循指挥棒的指引来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:03.50,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:05.96,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正在奏响的是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:07.88,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}余音缭绕的是情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:12.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:16.72,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的乐声将我们的泪水照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:21.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并非全是辛酸经历
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:26.70,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为　一路走来有许多快乐伴随着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:32.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！于五线谱之上唱响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:39.37,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！向着远处胜利的春天吹响吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望明日香学姐能站上全国大赛的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在那个音乐厅和学姐一起吹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要听学姐演奏的悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直在等明日香学姐你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大家也已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中同学她能够出席竞赛会了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:02:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来还是给大家添了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来到正赛为止  我会拼命练习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提高演奏水平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常一本正经的致辞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格转变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微变成熟点了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们的演奏有了很大的提高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但绝不能骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保持谦虚和进取心  努力练习到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入最后的冲刺阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:46.11,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}初恋的小号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子  该去组练了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总感觉她在避开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说是在无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你好像很高兴的样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说  一点头绪都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没觉得发生过什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说连一点迹象都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟之前明日香学姐的事已经够你操心的了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得直接去问她会比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但放学的时候总是碰不到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而早上来校也是各顾各的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非她是被人告白了  正在烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的  不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  难道她已经有恋人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子  这种时候需要开个作战会议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  退步到这种程度了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你带了慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs50\fsp3\c&H9394F1&\pos(742,326)}目标  全国!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是  逊毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很逊的学姐几乎没有看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可就看不到我这个样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂同学好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说我们3个这样等着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会像是在伏击她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和叶月躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自然点去和她打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呀丽奈…真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子  一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话  一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我有要事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被甩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子  快追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是不是遇到什么不开心的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:06:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得丽奈不会毫无理由就摆出那副态度的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈她其实挺难搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候会纠结一些小事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我并不是把错归咎于她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们错过绿灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次和她好好聊天是在什么时候来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是感冒休息的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一起回去的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄给妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭马上就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这信是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银行存折
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说自己开了账户  所以把这个还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要特意还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就说明姐姐她是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子  我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H505551&\fs50\frz340\pos(1498,122)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H505551&\fs50\frz340\pos(1374,352)}发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H505551&\fs50\frz338\pos(822,414)}我有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H505551&\fs50\frz338.5\pos(992,152)}我有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H505551&\fs50\frz338.5\pos(877,406)}待会儿能出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭的时候不要玩手机  你爸爸不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去大吉山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\bord0.5\1c&H201E18&\frz26\pos(896,600)\3c&HFFFFFF&}离\N别\N之\N树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我在生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我为什么生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…好像知道一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐约觉得是不是那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道的话就直说不知道不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想  我怎么可能知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是像平时那样和你说话的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更没有说过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样我才生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子  你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师妻子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在还泷老师钥匙的时候看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不住去确认了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  莫非是听黄前同学说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想你受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是希望你能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对自己的脆弱感到震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当听说他有妻子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我动摇到崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有察觉到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还对妈妈发火  质问她为什么一直没有告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我知道现在必须把精力集中在全国大赛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才把你叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在这里好好聊一聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后暂时忘记这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说这种话  可能又会被人说成性格糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的妻子已经去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:12:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈你是绝对不会理解我的心情的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你叫我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我家又不像你家一样有钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的儿子升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来父亲都承蒙您关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里  这话我说才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}长号…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等一会  我想我老公马上就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令尊还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要不断进取  上升的乐声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要演奏得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要走得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的乐声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有前辈批评我说  没有注意聆听周围人的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  那也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我觉得志向高远的心情也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更上一步  更上一层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  你知道这首曲子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的话就送给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经用不到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试着吹吹看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得它很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软弱无力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软弱无力  非常软弱无力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有集中精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有干劲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请立刻调整过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从H开始再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  不是能吹得很有力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近这阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没能集中精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织学姐也很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什么心事就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对我可能难以开口…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我会调整过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去还吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去老师那还钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天已经黑了  回去时要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量不要独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师的妻子是个怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从黄前同学那听来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你从黄前同学那听了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子以前是这所学校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经是吹奏部的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥本老师也和她一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我的父亲是这里的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要知道的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个充满活力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爱笑  很喜欢运动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说过自己的优点就是身体健康
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说将来要成为吹奏乐部的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带领大家打进全国
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当得知她时日不多的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脑袋变得一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  没过多久她就真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那泷老师来做吹奏部的顾问是为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她去世了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾有一段时间远离了吹奏乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都不想靠近乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  后来父亲让我来做顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我一直消沉下去  一定会惹她生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问那些事情  到头来受伤的只会是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢他妻子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢他妻子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了妻子成为顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了妻子想要去获得金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这个心情我想他应该是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟他们都结成夫妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:19:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  丽奈再也没有提起过这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表情没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乐声也毫不紊乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至吹奏出了更胜以往的强而有力的乐声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家尽量不要延误行动进程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请各位负责人集合一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认当天的行动安排
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上能陪我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在之前的地方见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再发消息联系你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:19:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我强求新山老师告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是泷老师妻子的墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从之前就一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我没有早点出生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我的时间能过的快点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上泷老师就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对泷老师的妻子说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拿下金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想替泷老师实现他的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要拿下金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
